Electronics Store Website
Project Overview
The Electronics Store Website is a front-end web development project created as part of my Information and Communication Technology (ICT) Lab course. The website simulates an online electronics shopping platform where users can browse electronic products through a simple, clean, and user-friendly interface.
The project focuses on learning the fundamentals of web development, webpage organization, navigation, and responsive page design using HTML.
Project Objective
The objectives of this project are to:
Design a responsive electronics shopping website.
Understand the structure of web pages using HTML.
Create an attractive and easy-to-use interface.
Organize products into different categories.
Improve front-end development skills.
