Conclusion
The Electronics Store Website successfully demonstrates the fundamentals of front-end web development by simulating an online electronics shopping platform. It provides an organized layout with product categories, navigation menus, and product information while emphasizing usability and clean design. This project strengthened my understanding of HTML, webpage structure, responsive design principles, and user interface development, providing a solid foundation for building more advanced web applications using CSS, JavaScript, and backend technologies in the future.
